snippet.textDisplay:
Actually kind of sad if they were at least well acquainted enough to be somewhat work buddies for at least that time. If they had at least a good working relationship and got along fine, just imagine how Jason might’ve felt when a lot of stuff was coming out about Amber in a bad light. For the cast and crew on any projects who’ve worked with her that did have a good opinion of her, this all had to be an uneasy feeling if not outright gut wrenching to face hearing the evidence against Ms.Heard. Her lack of self control with anger and her seemingly extreme lies have hurt a lot of people, herself, and especially Depp.

If I was Jason, I’d look back at these pics and be at least a little sad about what’s going on. I wouldn’t hate Heard, but it just wouldn’t sit well with me. I’d wanna work with her, but her actions would make it hard to look at her in a purely good light, but then I’d also fear how her presence in the sequel might ruin the films overall sales.
